        <mxCell id="efJcOQTv-WqSf4oPIb1X-59" value="&lt;b&gt;Why server do not has abilities to caculate secret of A and B&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;* server loss of neccessary datas to archive secret like private-key&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;*&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;ECDH bảo mật: biết pkA &amp;amp; pkB không suy ra skA hay skB.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;*&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;HKDF thêm một lớp “quay” HMAC, nên ngay cả khi một DH lộ vẫn không tách được toàn bộ dòng DH concat.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1139" y="203" width="460" height="104" as="geometry" />
