        <mxCell id="efJcOQTv-WqSf4oPIb1X-69" value="Each message : be Encrypted by a unique MK&lt;br&gt;N_s, N_r:&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Bộ đếm tin gửi (send) / nhận (recv) trong chuỗi hiện hành&lt;br&gt;gửi theo từng tin nhắn&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
